snippet: Five men who were arrested in Strasbourg and Marseille were directed by a commander in Iraq or Syria, the French authorities said Friday....
abstract: French authorities arrest five men on suspicion of plotting terrorist attack under direction of Islamic State commander; news increases anxiety in country that has been struck by three major terrorist attacks since January 2015.
lead_paragraph: Five men who were arrested in Strasbourg and Marseille were directed by a commander in Iraq or Syria, the French authorities said Friday.

headline.main: Prosecutor Says Arrests Disrupted ‘Imminent’ ISIS Attack in France
headline.print_headline: France Arrests Five Suspected of Plotting ‘Imminent’ Terrorist Attack
